About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. тАЬAlphaтАЭ, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: Saiyaara (1980) Ft. Kishore Kumar full song (Old version) Old is Gold with a New Voice!
snippet.description:
Saiyaara (1980) Ft. Kishore Kumar full song (Old version) Old is Gold with a New Voice!

Saiyaara (1980) тАУ Kishore Kumar's Saiyaara Full Song 
Step back in time and relive the golden era of Bollywood with Kishore Kumar's rare gem "Saiyaara" (1980). This soulful melody captures the essence of vintage romance, timeless lyrics, and the golden voice of Kishore Da that still resonates in every heart.

Whether you're a lifelong Kishore fan or discovering his magic for the first time, this song is a journey into the past that you don't want to mi

[Verse 1]
Tu paas hai mere paas hai aise
Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Tu paas hai mere paas hai aise
Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Baaton mein teri main raatein bitaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

[Chorus]
Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Verse 2]
Beetey lamhon se duniya basa loon
Main toh tere aansuon ka bana hoon

Meri hansi mein teri sadaayein
Teri kahaani khud ko sunaaun

Yaadon ke taare, yaadon ke taare tootenge kaise
Mere hain jo woh roothenge kaise

Beetey dinon ki kholi kitaabein
Guzre palon ko kaise bhula dein

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Baaton mein teri main raatein bitaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

[Chorus Repeat]
Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Bridge]
Jis roz hum tum phir se milenge
Yeh saari baatein tujhse kahenge

Duniya mein chaahe ban jaayein jo bhi
Tere bina tab kuch na rahenge

[Outro]
Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Main mar hi jaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon



ЁЯСЗ Let us know your favorite Kishore Kumar song in the comments! ЁЯСЗ

snippet.title: Divya is the champion!! | Tiebreaks | FIDE Women's World Cup 2025 ft. Sagar, Amruta, Harshit
snippet.description:
Kerala Chess Premier League: https://premierchessacademy.com/be-part-of-history-register-now-for-the-kerala-premier-chess-league-kpcl-2025/

Georgia holds a special place in the history of womenтАЩs chess, having produced some of the most legendary female players in the world.Batumi, known for its beautiful Black Sea coastline, is a fitting venue for this major tournament, which will gather the worldтАЩs top female chess players in a battle for glory.

What an incredible tournament has it been - and we have an All-Indian final on our hands! It is going to be IM Divya Deshmukh versus GM Koneru Humpy, a battle between youth and experience. Game 1 ended in an exciting draw, and also Game 2 had a similar result. It's now time for tiebreaks:

- 2 games of 15+10, in case of 1-1 tie 
- 2 games of 10+10, in case of 1-1 tie
- 2 games of 5+3, in case of 1-1 tie
- 1 games of 3+2 and in case of a draw, another game of 3+2 until a winner is found.

IM Sagar Shah, Amruta Mokal and GM Harshit Raja will be doing the live commentary

Video: ChessBase India

snippet.description:
ЁЯЩП рдзрди-рдзрди рд╕рддрдЧреБрд░реБ | рдЬрдп рдЬреЛрд╣рд╛рд░, рдЬрдп рдЖрджрд┐рд╡рд╛рд╕реА ЁЯМ┐
Aadiwood Production (The Brand of Nimar) proudly presents "Asli Aadiwasi" - a brand-new video song teaser in the powerful voices of Bheem Kanoje and Pradnya Jadhav. localized.description:
ЁЭРАЁЭРЛЁЭРБЁЭРФЁЭРМ ЁЭРНЁЭРАЁЭРМЁЭРД : ЁЭРНЁЭРЪЁЭРаЁЭРоЁЭРеЁЭРЪЁЭРЬЁЭРбЁЭРЪЁЭРпЁЭРвЁЭРнЁЭРбЁЭРв ЁЭРТЁЭРйЁЭРЮЁЭРЬЁЭРвЁЭРЪЁЭРе ЁЭРТЁЭРиЁЭРзЁЭРаЁЭРм ЁЭЯРЁЭЯОЁЭЯРЁЭЯУ

ЁЭРЛЁЭРШЁЭРСЁЭРИЁЭРВЁЭРТ : ЁЭРЙЁЭРАЁЭРНЁЭРЖЁЭРИ ЁЭРСЁЭРДЁЭРГЁЭРГЁЭРШ & ЁЭРМЁЭРАЁЭРГЁЭРГЁЭРИЁЭРНЁЭРДЁЭРНЁЭРИ ЁЭРТЁЭРСЁЭРИЁЭРНЁЭРИЁЭРХЁЭРАЁЭРТ

ЁЭРТЁЭРИЁЭРНЁЭРЖЁЭРДЁЭРС  : ЁЭРЙЁЭРЪЁЭРзЁЭРаЁЭРв ЁЭРСЁЭРЮЁЭРЭЁЭРЭЁЭР▓, ЁЭРАЁЭРдЁЭРоЁЭРзЁЭРоЁЭРлЁЭРв ЁЭРГЁЭРЮЁЭРпЁЭРЪЁЭР▓ЁЭР▓ЁЭРЪ, ЁЭРСЁЭРЪЁЭРжЁЭРЪЁЭРЭЁЭРЮЁЭРпЁЭРв, ЁЭРЙЁЭРЪЁЭРЭЁЭРЪЁЭРеЁЭРЪ ЁЭРСЁЭРЪЁЭРжЁЭРЮЁЭРмЁЭРб, ЁЭРХЁЭРЪЁЭРЭЁЭРеЁЭРЪЁЭРдЁЭРиЁЭРзЁЭРЭЁЭРЪ ЁЭРАЁЭРзЁЭРвЁЭРеЁЭРдЁЭРоЁЭРжЁЭРЪЁЭРл,

ЁЭРМЁЭРФЁЭРТЁЭРИЁЭРВ : ЁЭРЖЁЭРЛ ЁЭРНЁЭРАЁЭРМЁЭРГЁЭРДЁЭРХ

ЁЭРМЁЭРФЁЭРТЁЭРИЁЭРВ ЁЭРОЁЭРН : ЁЭЧйЁЭЧаЁЭЧЦ ЁЭЧЧЁЭЧШЁЭЧйЁЭЧвЁЭЧзЁЭЧЬЁЭЧвЁЭЧбЁЭЧФЁЭЧЯ ЁЭЧжЁЭЧвЁЭЧбЁЭЧЪЁЭЧж

ЁЭРТЁЭРФЁЭРБЁЭРТЁЭРВЁЭРСЁЭРИЁЭРБЁЭРД ЁЭРЕЁЭРОЁЭРС ЁЭРМЁЭРОЁЭРСЁЭРД ЁЭРХЁЭРМЁЭРВ ЁЭРГЁЭРДЁЭРХЁЭРОЁЭРУЁЭРИЁЭРОЁЭРНЁЭРАЁЭРЛ ЁЭРТЁЭРОЁЭРНЁЭРЖЁЭРТ : https://www.youtube.com/@VMCDEVOTIONAL
